  "detailed_description": "In this platform game you will have to overcome challenging puzzles using a weapon capable of rewinding the time of an object.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Objects</h2>Destroy and rebuild objects to overcome obstacles, press buttons or block enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/06e003ba9c7dbd32a30ed6fe5ebb1f69.avif?t=1623745310\" width=609 height=271 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2>Harness the power of your weapon to control enemies and eliminate them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/ec2341bdf67cc26d485dbf08cb8ab940.avif?t=1623745310\" width=694 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skeletons </h2>Revive skeletons to use as bait or to press buttons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/1e034c8cc7333238f71a492d059ffc7c.avif?t=1623745310\" width=715 height=183 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Traps</h2>Overcome ingenious traps of various types also thanks to your weapon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/d9b3a809de14f3223c9ed03e2a8ec0cc.avif?t=1623745310\" width=652 height=500 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "In this platform game you will have to overcome challenging puzzles using a weapon capable of rewinding the time of an object.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Objects</h2>Destroy and rebuild objects to overcome obstacles, press buttons or block enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/06e003ba9c7dbd32a30ed6fe5ebb1f69.avif?t=1623745310\" width=609 height=271 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2>Harness the power of your weapon to control enemies and eliminate them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/ec2341bdf67cc26d485dbf08cb8ab940.avif?t=1623745310\" width=694 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skeletons </h2>Revive skeletons to use as bait or to press buttons.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/1e034c8cc7333238f71a492d059ffc7c.avif?t=1623745310\" width=715 height=183 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Traps</h2>Overcome ingenious traps of various types also thanks to your weapon.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1586510/extras/d9b3a809de14f3223c9ed03e2a8ec0cc.avif?t=1623745310\" width=652 height=500 /></span>",
